/li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Escape_from_Dragonstone_by_Allen_Douglas_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Escape_from_Dragonstone_by_Allen_Douglas_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/300px-Escape_from_Dragonstone_by_Allen_Douglas_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"399\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Escape_from_Dragonstone_by_Allen_Douglas_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/450px-Escape_from_Dragonstone_by_Allen_Douglas_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Escape_from_Dragonstone_by_Allen_Douglas_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/600px-Escape_from_Dragonstone_by_Allen_Douglas_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Escape_from_Dragonstone_by_Allen_Douglas_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Alyssa Velaryon, Jaehaerys Targaryen, and Alysanne Targaryen escape Dragonstone by Allen Douglas for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Year 44 After the Conquest</b> (<b>44 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 44th after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maesters</a> and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>44 AC was peaceful compared to the previous one, and with the pregnancy of Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Harroway\" title=\"Alys Harroway\">Alys Harroway</a>, it seemed as if King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor</a> would finally get his much desired heir. However, after three months Alys gave birth to a stillborn monstrosity, and Maegor angrily ordered the executions of those in her care, including <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Desmond_(Grand_Maester)\" title=\"Desmond (Grand Maester)\">Desmond</a>. Afterwards, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Tyanna_of_the_Tower\" title=\"Tyanna of the Tower\">Tyanna of the Tower</a> approached Maegor and accused Alys of having laid with many men to get pregnant. After obtaining confessions under <a href=\"/index.php/Torture\" title=\"Torture\">torture</a>, Maegor executed Alys, her father the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hand\">Hand</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harroway\" title=\"House Harroway\">their family</a>, and the alleged lovers. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Towers\" title=\"Walton Towers\">Walton Towers</a> was named the new <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Lord of Harrenhal\">Lord of Harrenhal</a> after winning a <a href=\"/index.php/Melee\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Melee\">melee</a> of Maelor's <a href=\"/index.php/Household_knight\" title=\"Household knight\">household knights</a>, though he died of his wounds within two weeks of the event. Walton's son <a href=\"/index.php/Jordan_Towers\" title=\"Jordan Towers\">Jordan Towers</a> received Harrenhal, though not all of the lands formerly belonging to House Harroway, as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Harroway%27s_Town\" title=\"Lord Harroway&#39;s Town\">Lord Harroway's Town</a> was granted to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alton_Butterwell\" title=\"Alton Butterwell\">Alton Butterwell</a> and the rest of the Harroway holdings to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Darnold_Darry\" title=\"Darnold Darry\">Darnold Darry</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Later in the year, Dowager Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a> died, and Dowager Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> took the opportunity to flee into hiding, with her children <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne</a> and their <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>, as well as Visenya's <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Sword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sword\">sword</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Dark_Sister\" title=\"Dark Sister\">Dark Sister</a>. In rage, Maegor had Alyssa's eldest living son, his <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Hostage\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hostage\">hostage</a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen_(son_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen (son of Aenys I)\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, tortured for nine days until the prince died. His body was left in the courtyard for a fortnight, in the hopes that his mother would claim it, but Alyssa did not return.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Births\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Births</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Deaths\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Deaths</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=44_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The entire <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harroway\" title=\"House Harroway\">House Harroway</a> is obliterated on King Maegor's orders.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>A melee is held in <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Harroway%27s_Town\" title=\"Lord Harroway&#39;s Town\">Lord Harroway's Town</a> to decide the new ruler of <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/House_Towers\" title=\"House Towers\">House Towers</a> receives Harrenhal, but <a href=\"/index.php/House_Butterwell\" title=\"House Butterwell\">House Butterwell</a> receives Lord Harroway's Town and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">House Darry</a> receives the rest of their lands.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edwell_Celtigar\" title=\"Edwell Celtigar\">Edwell Celtigar</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, replacing Lord Lucas Harroway.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Following the death of Dowager Queen Visenya, Dowager Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> flees <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> with her youngest two living children, <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne</a>, and their <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vermithor\" title=\"Vermithor\">Vermithor</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Silverwing\" title=\"Silverwing\">Silverwing</a>. Alyssa takes the Valyrian sword <a href=\"/index.php/Dark_Sister\" title=\"Dark Sister\">Dark Sister</a> with her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Births\">Births</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=44_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Births\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Arryn\" title=\"Rodrik Arryn\">Rodrik Arryn</a>, son of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rymond_Arryn\" title=\"Rymond Arryn\">Rymond Arryn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=44_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Pater\" title=\"Pater\">Septon Pater</a>, the aged man who became <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a> after his predecessor's death the previous year.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Harroway\" title=\"Alys Harroway\">Alys Harroway</a>, put to death by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lucas_Harroway\" title=\"Lucas Harroway\">Lucas Harroway</a>, put to death by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Harroway\" title=\"Jeyne Harroway\">Jeyne Harroway</a>, put to death by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Hanna_Harroway\" title=\"Hanna Harroway\">Hanna Harroway</a>, put to death by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Horas_Harroway\" title=\"Horas Harroway\">Horas Harroway</a>, put to death by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Every living member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harroway\" title=\"House Harroway\">House Harroway</a> was ordered to be put to death by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Desmond_(Grand_Maester)\" title=\"Desmond (Grand Maester)\">Desmond</a>, put to death by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Dowager Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a>, on <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen_(son_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen (son of Aenys I)\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, tortured and murdered on the orders of <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor the Cruel</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Tyanna\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tyanna\">Tyanna</a> of the Tower.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Towers\" title=\"Walton Towers\">Walton Towers</a> died from his wounds received in the melee for the castle of <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf43.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-14\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=44_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\">1.10</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\">1.11</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B